&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;h4 id=&quot;food-power-ferocity&quot;&gt;Food (Power&#x2F;Ferocity):&lt;&#x2F;h4&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;items&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;91805&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Cilantro Lime Sous-Vide Steak&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;items&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;41569&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Bowl of Sweet and Spicy Butternut Squash Soup (Budget Alternative)&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;ul&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;h4 id=&quot;consumable-power&quot;&gt;Consumable (Power):&lt;&#x2F;h4&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
